The following folder contains solution for PreppinData Week 3 challenge. The challenge focuses on data preparation using unions, pivots and aggregation.
"PD 2021 Wk 2 Input - Bike Model Sales" is the input file on which data cleaning and transformation is to be performed.
"Week 2 Challenge Flow" is the flow created in Tableau Prep to solve the problem
"Sales by Brand & Bike Type" & "Sales by Brand & Store" are the outputs to be used for comparison.
Also, please check out the "Week2 flow image" for reference and check out the blog @ https://vizartpandey.com/tableau-prep-challenge-s02e02/
